title: Positive players are welcome
body:
Hey guys just started a new club called Narwhals{{sticker:galio-happy}}  ( it's an animal people sometimes called unicorn of the sea) positive players are hard to find so I want to have a club for positive players to join.

If you are not toxic players and would like to join my club, feel free to add me and let me know you would like to join the club.
Leave a message and sum name below if you would like to join the club. 
Let's all the unicorn of the sea guys! :) {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 
sum name: snakecamel
